tonight:

00:09.109 --> 00:11.245 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BILL DE BLASIO (D), Mayor of New
York: We
have every right to believe this
was an act

00:11.278 --> 00:12.246 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
terror.

00:12.279 --> 00:14.414 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Security on high
alert.

00:14.448 --> 00:19.753 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
