his motive.

01:12.172 --> 01:17.511 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
An arrest this morning in New
Jersey has ended
a manhunt in a series of
bombings and attempted

01:17.544 --> 01:20.280 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
bombings around New York City
and New Jersey.

01:20.314 --> 01:22.249 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MAN: That's definitely him.

01:22.282 --> 01:28.488 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Ahmad Khan Rahami
was loaded into
an ambulance, bloody and dazed
after a gun

01:28.522 --> 01:30.390 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
battle with police.

01:30.424 --> 01:36.563 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
