citizen from
Afghanistan was captured in
Linden, New Jersey,

01:36.596 --> 01:40.634 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
after he was recognized sleeping
in the doorway
of a bar.

01:40.667 --> 01:45.939 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That was just hours after police
sent text
alerts to millions in the New
York metro area

01:45.973 --> 01:47.908 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
to be on the lookout for him.

01:47.941 --> 01:52.412 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
After the shoot-out, in which
two police officers
and the suspect were injured,
New York City

01:52.446 --> 01:55.949 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Mayor Bill de Blasio firmly
labeled the bombings
terrorism.

01:55.983 --> 01:58.919 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BILL DE BLASIO (D), Mayor of New
York: We
have so more much information
obviously than

01:58.952 --> 02:01.521 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
we even had a few hours ago.

02:01.555 --> 02:05.959 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Based on the information we have
now, we have
every reason to believe this was
an act of

02:05.993 --> 02:07.794 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
terror.

02:07.828 --> 02:12.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: It all began on
Saturday morning
in a bomb attack in the beach
town of Seaside

02:12.399 --> 02:17.104 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Park, New Jersey, before a
charity race to
benefit Marines.

02:17.137 --> 02:18.972 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
No one was injured there.

02:19.006 --> 02:24.144 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Later that night, in the Chelsea
neighborhood
of Manhattan, another bomb went
off, injuring

02:24.177 --> 02:25.512 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
29 people.

02:25.545 --> 02:30.117 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Surveillance video allegedly
caught Rahami
planting the device.

02:30.150 --> 02:35.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A second device, made from a
pressure cooker
filled with shrapnel, was found
undetonated

02:35.422 --> 02:37.657 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
a few blocks away.

02:37.691 --> 02:42.295 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And last night, five more pipe
bombs were
found at a train station in
Elizabeth, New

02:42.329 --> 02:43.597 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Jersey.

02:43.630 --> 02:50.037 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
As robots worked to dismantle
them, one exploded
suddenly.

02:50.070 --> 02:54.641 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Officials linked all of the
attacks to Rahami,
but offered limited details
about how they

02:54.674 --> 02:56.410 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
made that connection.

02:56.443 --> 03:01.081 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, with Rahami as a named
suspect, police
descended on his family home in
Elizabeth.

03:01.114 --> 03:04.818 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MAN: He's a very friendly guy.

03:04.851 --> 03:05.819 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That's what's so scary.

03:05.852 --> 03:06.820 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It's hard when it's home.

03:06.853 --> 03:07.821 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
They never seemed out of the
ordinary.

03:07.854 --> 03:09.856 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They were just Americanized.

03:09.890 --> 03:12.926 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You would have never known
anything.

03:12.959 --> 03:19.199 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: At a midday press
conference,
an FBI official said the agency
cannot yet

03:19.232 --> 03:23.503 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
say why Rahami planted the
bombs, but that
he appeared to have acted alone.

03:23.537 --> 03:27.607 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BILL SWEENEY, FBI: I have no
indication that
there is a cell operating in the
area or in

03:27.641 --> 03:29.376 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
