weighed in from
New York, where he's attending
the United

03:38.485 --> 03:40.320 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Nations General Assembly.

03:40.353 --> 03:44.157 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA, President of the
United States:
Even as we have to be vigilant
and aggressive,

03:44.191 --> 03:50.697 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
both in preventing senseless
acts of violence,
but also making sure that we
find those who

03:50.730 --> 03:57.737 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
carry out such acts and bring
them to justice,
we all have a role to play as
citizens in

03:57.771 --> 03:59.706 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
making sure that we don't
succumb to that
fear.

03:59.739 --> 04:03.844 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: In the wake of the
attacks and
with hundreds of world leaders
converging

04:03.877 --> 04:11.351 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
on the city, police and
bomb-sniffing dogs
swarmed New York's Penn Station
today.

04:11.384 --> 04:15.755 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
