today.

04:18.792 --> 04:22.896 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He was shot in the leg during
and the arm
during the shoot-out with
police.

04:22.929 --> 04:26.299 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
