college student
from Somalia.

04:49.389 --> 04:55.462 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: The Syrian military
declared today
that a week-long cease-fire is
over, and within

04:55.495 --> 04:57.631 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
