refused to concede the truce is
dead.

05:09.943 --> 05:15.749 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN KERRY, U.S. Secretary of
State: The Russians
need to control Assad, who
evidently is indiscriminately

05:15.782 --> 05:18.218 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
