then we will
make a judgment.

05:25.725 --> 05:31.298 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Activists said the
various airstrikes
killed more than 30 people,
including a dozen

05:31.331 --> 05:33.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
