planes carried
out an airstrike there aimed at
Taliban forces.

05:51.151 --> 05:56.523 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: In Russia,
supporters of President
Vladimir Putin won a landslide
in Sunday's

05:56.556 --> 05:58.358 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
