06:36.763 --> 06:41.167 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Signs of progress
today against
the Zika outbreak in Miami,
Florida.

06:41.201 --> 06:45.372 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Health officials dropped their
warning to
pregnant women to avoid the
city's Wynwood

06:45.405 --> 06:46.806 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
arts district.

06:46.840 --> 06:50.644 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
