political motives,
a certain neighborhood in New
York, the Marine

09:20.994 --> 09:23.229 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Corps marathon.

09:23.263 --> 09:25.031 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
