picture of
somebody that had some signs of
radicalization.

09:29.002 --> 09:33.139 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Juliette Kayyem,
what do you
make of this, the sophistication
of it, how

09:33.173 --> 09:35.008 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
