percent success
rate.

09:53.927 --> 09:59.365 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so what I'm curious about
is, how quick
was that radicalization process,
that, you

09:59.399 --> 10:03.336 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
