number of people
involved in the action?

10:06.706 --> 10:10.877 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think that that is going to be
relevant
to determine whether it's just
him, him and

10:10.910 --> 10:12.946 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
