about what was
agreed to?

28:17.262 --> 28:20.098 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FILIPPO GRANDI, United Nations
High Commissioner
for Refugees: Yes.

28:20.132 --> 28:26.805 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The General Assembly, meaning
all the states
in the world, have issued a
declaration which

28:26.838 --> 28:33.845 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
