New York Declaration,
committing themselves to
protecting, assisting

28:33.879 --> 28:41.286 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
refugees, but also finding new
ways the organize
better the response to refugee
crisis.

28:41.320 --> 28:46.191 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, you know, for a long time,
we have struggled
with the resources.

28:46.224 --> 28:52.331 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
