expand our support
to them that this declaration
will help us

29:05.210 --> 29:07.045 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
carry out.

29:07.079 --> 29:10.716 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Obviously, a
global agreement
of this kind is important, but
this agreement

29:10.749 --> 29:14.820 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
