there is a lot
of political weight behind that.

29:31.370 --> 29:36.074 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And then I think that, also,
everybody has
realized -- especially when
refugees in the

29:36.108 --> 29:41.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
